OL,5, Football clubs should think about the  
OL,6, impact on fans when accepting          
OL,7, sponsorships from gambling firms, the  
OL,8, head of NHS England has said.          
OL,10,FAmanda Pritchard said the deals send a 
OL,11,Fmessage that "gambling is OK".         
OL,13,FHer comments came after the news that  
OL,14,Fthe NHS is nearly doubling the number  
OL,15,Fof gambling addiction clinics to 15    
OL,16,Fafter a record number of referrals.    
OL,18,FSome 1,389 patients were referred for  
OL,19,Fgambling support in 2022-23, up from   
OL,20,F775 two years prior.                   
